title: The Jboy Show - Would you rather have Jimbo or Lane?

description:
Jboy discusses the latest news on the college football playoff, plus debates whether he would want Jimbo Fisher or Lane Kiffin to lead his program. Make sure to check us out LIVE on Youtube every day at 3pm EST, plus follow us @thejboyshow on all social media platforms.
